The paper also involves the use of clustering algorithms and techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DB (Databases) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). 

Furthermore, the paper discusses the use of data-driven insights, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
